                <th id="th">The most common causes of scheduling changes in launches</th>
                <td id="td">

                    - Technical problems can appear all of a sudden, even in the last moments before the flight. Those cannot be overlooked due to the damage they can do to the mission, no matter how insignificant they seem to be.
